        Military-grade AI algorithms and real-time market intelligence for superior trading performance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- AI Surveillance Card -->
      <div class="group relative bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700 hover:border-cyan-400/50 rounded-2xl p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400/5 to-blue-500/5 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(60, 158, 254), rgb(113, 126, 251)); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(60, 158, 254, 0.3);">
            <.icon name="hero-eye-solid" class="size-7 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Omnipresent AI</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            24/7 market surveillance with pattern recognition, anomaly detection, and predictive modeling.
          </p>
